Tablets

Class Tablet

  • java.lang.Object
    • Tablets.Tablet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TabletRelatable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GalaxyTablet, iPadTablet, NexusTablet

    public abstract class Tablet
extends java.lang.Object
implements TabletRelatable
    Abstract super class that virtualizes the the generic characteristics of a tablet device.

        Specified by:

        Parameters:

        Returns:
